    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He gave him the-- he was bloody, this-- this was-- this was-- this was stories which-- which you can tell and tell.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then once they brought in [SIGHS] a small transport to-- a-- a-- a transport.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There came SS with-- with the-- with the-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- those-- [NON-ENGLISH] You know what it means, the hats?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- the black-- black-- it was-- Like a beret?",
